Below are incorrect uses, anti-patterns, and bad practices for the `<{{componentName}}>` component.

## 1. <!-- imperative title, e.g. "Do Not Slot HTML Elements" -->

<!-- One sentence: WHY this is wrong (what breaks, accessibility issue, etc.). -->

```html
<!-- 🚫 INCORRECT -->
<{{componentName}}><!-- the wrong usage --></{{componentName}}>

<!-- ✅ CORRECT -->
<{{componentName}}><!-- the right usage --></{{componentName}}>
```

## 2. <!-- imperative title -->

<!-- One sentence: WHY this is wrong. -->

```html
<!-- 🚫 INCORRECT -->
<{{componentName}}></{{componentName}}>

<!-- ✅ CORRECT -->
<{{componentName}}></{{componentName}}>
```

